Step 1: In a medium saucepan, add potatoes and cover with water. Bring to a boil over high heat. Reduce heat to low and simmer 20 minutes or until potatoes are very tender; drain. In same saucepan, melt Becel(R) Buttery Taste margarine over medium heat and cook garlic, stirring for 1 minute or until fragrant. Step 2: Return potatoes to saucepan; mash. Stir in remaining ingredients. Nutritional Facts Calories (Kcals): 180 % Daily Value Total Fat: 6g Saturated fat: 1g Trans Fat: 0g Polyunsaturates: 1.8g Omega-6: 1.4g Omega-3: 0.4g Monounsaturates: 2.8g 9% 5% Cholesterol:0mg 0% Sodium:80mg 3% Potassium: 814mg 16% Total Carbohydrate: 28g Dietary Fibre: 3g Sugars: 3g 9% 12% Protein: 4g Vitamin A: 8% Vitamin C: 30% Calcium: 4% Iron: 8% Preparation Time: 15 minutes Cook Time: 25 minutes Total Time: 40 minutes http://www.becel.ca/en/becel/HeartHealthyRecipes/Side-Dishes/Garlic-Parsley-Mashed-Potatoes.aspx